Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯獨不想被鮎澤討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 就知道說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直拿我開玩笑 真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 本來還有些感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺也會忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:02:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還沒好好答謝你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不用謝謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論幾次我都會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論幾次 我都會讓你喜歡上我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說些…什麼…蠢話…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23小時55分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只剩下5分鐘 但看來還是我贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護會長的騎士一職
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸你還是退下的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被討厭的話 連這種小遊戲都會變得無趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想認真跟我玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 現在才想嚇唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了碓冰的變態白癡台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越感覺煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有心情睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你整到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也懶得管你為什麼討厭女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你嚐嚐我秘藏的懲罰技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:32.25,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,145)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\c&HCCF7FD&}{\3c&H2B367B&}{\shad0}{\bord2}校園參觀會上的眼鏡兔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}校園參觀會通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校園參觀會的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向國中三年級生 每年都有辦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝負的時刻就要到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將強者納入手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出未來的王牌選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動社團的盛衰從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是假日舉辦 主要是社團活動介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們都沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今年除了社團活動介紹之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有很多活動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5\pos(180,57)}會長致詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13\pos(260,137)}社團嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\pos(640,107)}星華高中七大不可思議介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七大不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\pos(600,183)}治癒點介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂人員？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好玩的樣子 食堂系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:11.88,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,10)}系？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:11.88,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,10)}三笨蛋說的才是正確唸法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年舉辦很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀路線中 想設一個可愛的食堂來做休息所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那裡佈置成連國中女生也能安心休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合女生的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備起來應該會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能夠幫我嗎 我需要人手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟其他女生說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待那些國中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裝飾些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要想一下預算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 應該會有些力氣活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也指望不了其他男生來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的葉爽太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因某些原因 現在是學生會的雜工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是蓋著遮風帽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是一年級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那總之先去集合人手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從什麼開始著手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從房間裝飾開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉 葉君 雖然不清楚原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要好好幫忙做食堂的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長說以前的事就一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,140)\frz-80}抖抖抖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是副會長幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.67,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,260)}食堂負責人 兼 葉監視人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君 這邊的東西幫忙搬一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 用這個的話 這邊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用化學室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該不在食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用催眠術…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長到底有幾個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有分裂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人哦 應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 這樣看著葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得哪裡不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是躲著女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是敵視的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又不是女性過敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那面牆壁不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 絆到椅子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小美又休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 小美在不在我們都要來光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才叫真正的愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 確實 碓冰也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊 這是抽獎中的鬱金茶和栗子羊羹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 放那邊就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做校園參觀會的準備？很拼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗奈覺得怎樣的學校你才會想進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准說有抽獎社的高中哦 除此之外都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:38.54,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物徵集社
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 你就只知道這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.65,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀會前一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君 再右邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點歪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有在努力嘛 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲同學 你來看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想服裝就用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很用心準備的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也說很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 這樣…這樣不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 放開手辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.60,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…於是當天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是校內參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 分成好多路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校內參觀由在校生做嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人想看到的星華高中肯定不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇自己感興趣的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.74,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高中對社團感興趣的請到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.27,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化社是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.53,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術社在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有治癒點路線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七大不可思議巡遊路線…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提 不知怎麼選擇路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想全部體驗的人請到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問問題也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那第一組出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 麻煩來一個人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那我們也出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨問隨答路線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小美果然也是休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天其實不用來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 要我講幾次才明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管小美在不在都要來光顧 才是真正的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 連碓冰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了呢 各位主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們果然只被當可憐人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天小美休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是女僕拿鐵的其餘女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將難得地全員出動為各位服務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺飄飄欲仙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄起來了 飄起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特別為各位介紹今天的廚房人員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千和小糯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝平日的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 第一次出大堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道該說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好不是神秘生物體在做料理之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 來狂點餐囉 我付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要在客人留言上盡情傾訴我的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 很好 小郁 fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我寫上噁心的…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是氣勢恢宏的詩詞 滿滿滿滿地寫進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把跟小美充滿回憶的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在腦內來個走馬燈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替您寫上了「很煩」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會造成其他主人的困擾 可以安靜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用再回來了哦 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候能聽到她溫柔的話語就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星華高中七大不可思議之二是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理應無人的廣播室裡 突然播放音樂的怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.14,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.51,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動播放設定之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前看來都很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 運動社團就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.50,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用拳套打沙袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用擒抱來親密接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟球做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是在做無用功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭呢 這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很閒的話也不用週末特地來學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣說 我在幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,380)}邪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當會長的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在比較放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在的話大家都會分心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太顯眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你要這麼說我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(100,380)}邪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有份差事一定要你做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有半個人想跟球做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊被擊沉的足球社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰說他無論如何都想跟球做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我還是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 碓冰同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請請請 這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來個超帥的射門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球衣也穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種中學小弟小妹 馬上就能看到超精彩的球技哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球社 碓冰學長在幫忙拉人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也幫我們社團拉人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 為了星華幫運動社炒熱氣氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍 稍等 我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會接客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:47.41,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實已經準備好葉君的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊們自己玩高興就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那麼淒涼的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得大家一起努力到現在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 一起盡興到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 葉君幫了很多忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一開始經常落跑的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接客我們來 端盤子之類的一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事我們會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 幸村也很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 準備了很適合葉君的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你們也一起來踢足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和足球做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰同學 接下來是我們棒球社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他想看的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 在美術室裡接觸到了各種畫材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在音樂室第一次彈了吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到能如此大開眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 開開心心地參觀到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌球社 也請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:16.28,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來參觀的天才桌球少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪條線路最後都是到食堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家走累了 休息之餘順便也來個最後提問時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去跟其他前輩聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨便坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像女僕咖啡店一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 哇 你看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛啊 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲也一起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 看起來很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也有被嚇跑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過搭上話他們就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 說實話最初以為會被男生嘲笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到氣氛很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論男女 都會很高興地聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的氣氛變成日常的話 一定會很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同擁有愉快的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是一件很美好的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去看看其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這麼可愛的角色了啊 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法啊 被那麼多女的圍著根本沒辦法逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 難道被扒得光光…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說討厭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼很合適我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可愛的帽子是什麼啊 當我是兔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人到底什麼眼光啊 女僕裝為什麼能那麼輕飄飄的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼啊 那種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 果然對女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種生物 肯定會輕易就壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉 你和以前比 現在能看著對方眼睛說話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天應該看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像你想的那樣 她們柔弱易碎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該面對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣和女生在一起 還是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(730,180)}亂入的中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.00,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了高中生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰同學 接下去是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 碓冰同學 幫一下我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們社
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先來我們這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.01,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考考看星華吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 想進我們學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太歡迎了 你們喜歡星華啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不過 還是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我很怕男生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前一直讀的都是女校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是陪我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星華男生很多吧 是女校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你說媽媽崩潰了離家出走是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽太郎 女人比想像中還要纖細脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和女人打交道時也要注意一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(700,340)}父 原摔跤手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會壞掉的話 我就不接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.17,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 母親只是受夠了父親而離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在收盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不想再接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦接近 也許又會像那時候一樣受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為女人很柔弱 易碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像你想的那樣 她們柔弱易碎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕男生啊 就這個有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 眼鏡兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓她不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該面對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要施展魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再對男生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會用那麼可愛的魔法啊 眼鏡兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬完這個就可以收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信守約定 之前的事一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去時候小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 會長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 辛苦你了 碓冰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備去哪啊 能放下我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說話啊 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了？懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那接下來慰勞一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都沒來看過我 啊 累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 全託碓冰的福 運動社盛況空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了 感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做一些 別人對你做你會高興的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮎澤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能推倒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村學長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 真的最尊敬的就是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒發覺你是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想換衣服 制服找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(630,190)}(渚(24)\N五月的妹妹\N海之家 beach house 店長)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不停地動來動去 就不會想睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉要給會長施催眠術的話 催眠點別的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人可以1個月左右不睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那麼我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別當真啊 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:23:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很唐突 下集講夏天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美 女僕拿鐵的大家要一起去海之家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 泳裝都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰 就拜託你當保鏢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:10.67,biaoti2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(750,357)}{\c&H509EF5&}{\fad(300,0)}海之家也是女僕拿鐵
